title: CYO-MATEYO
synopsis: This is the story of a girl who wanders into the world of doujinshi (fanzines), a comical and chaotic 2,5D world. We invite you to such a world! Why don't you take a trip through the world of doujinshi with us? "Welcome to the world of doujinshi!"
